== DeJoan Blair == DeJoan Blair hya'ga NBA pgnaw' mari' misow qaniy, qotox sa pzyang pkaki' tay kska' / pkaki' kkska'. kawas te 1989, byacing te 4 ro 22 ryax qo hintgan nya, kinholan nya ga Pennsylvania, hiya ga mnanak na ppzoy mari waya, ro sqoliq ka ppkal mari waya. 201 konbon kinwagiq nya, 122 konkin kin'sow nya, hiya ga qotox nqo spzyang blaq na ppzoy mari NBA. kawas 2009 mnwayaw ppzoy mari ga, mzyop sqo te qotox lahoy ro te magal sqoliq, galon nqo San Antonio Spors. pincyowagan nya' cinkholan sa knita' sa brbiro' Lists of National Basketball Association players
